column5: Looking for a firewood supplier in the Burke falls or sundridge area lost the contact info for my regular guy.  Thanks for any help
I got one,but will have to wait til I get home to get the number. My pop has it, the guy is in Burksfalls  Oh I got it  Rick  705 382 3721
Thanks a lot.  I appreciate the info!!!  If your in the area from feb 6 - 10.  Let me know   We are going to be fishing Bernard all weekend.  Maybey little doe as well
